<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hoodwink" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hoodwink,</orth> to blindfold: <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.26" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 6, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.1.90" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 90</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 2, 16</bibl>. Used strangely by Caliban: <cit><quote>the prize I'll bring thee to shall h. this mischance,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.206" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 206</bibl></cit>, == shall make harmless, ineffectual.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>